### New `Secrets/EncryptedSecretProvider.php`
Implements `SecretProviderInterface` to allow storing encrypted passwords directly in the tenant record:
```php
public function getDatabasePassword(Tenant $tenant): string
{
    return $this->encryption->decrypt($tenant->encryptedDatabasePassword);
}
```
This is the recommended provider for auto-provisioned tenants.

