## 10. Logging

All provisioning classes accept a `Psr\Log\LoggerInterface`. The recommended channel name is `tenant-provisioning`.

Log points:
- `info`: database created, user created, schema installed, seeding started, admin created, pages created
- `debug`: SQL executed, bootstrap path
- `error`: any caught exception with `tenant_id`, step name, elapsed time
- `notice`: retry attempts

